The evidence with the title 'Obamacare robs medicare of $716 billion to Fund Itself ' says Aug 1, 2012  ... Last week , a new Congressional Budget Office (CBO) report updated the amount of money Obamacare robs out of Medicare from $ 500 billion to a whopping $716 billion between 2013 and 2022 . According to the CBO, the payment cuts in Medicare include : a $260 billion payment cut for hospital services. 
